org.obrel.space

Interface ObjectSpace<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Relatable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FileSystemSpace, HtmlSpace, MappedSpace, RelationSpace, SynchronizedObjectSpace

    public interface ObjectSpace<T>
extends Relatable
    An interface that defines hierarchical spaces of relatable objects which can be accessed with URLs. For readonly variants only the get(String) method must be implemented. The modifying methods put(String, Object) and delete(String) have default implementations that throw an UnsupportedOperationException.
